  {
    "content_id": 419441,
    "reference_id": 109040,
    "title": "Yakobo 1:19–27",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "59001019-59001027",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Kila kitu ambacho <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108302\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">watu wa Mungu</span> wanafikiria, kuamini, kusema na kufanya lazima kikubaliane na <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108200\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">neno la Mungu</span>. Hii ikitokea, waumini wanaishi maisha <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108361\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">matakatifu</span>.</p><p><span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108044\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">Maisha matakatifu</span> yanategemea kumsikiliza Mungu kwa makini. Yanategemea kutii mafundisho ya kweli kuhusu Mungu. Yakobo alielezea hili kama kujifunza sheria inayotoa uhuru. Hiyo ni njia nyingine ya kuzungumzia <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108147\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">sheria ya Kristo</span>.</p><p>Ni <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108165\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">kamilifu</span>. Inatoa uhuru kwa sababu <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108219\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">Yesu</span> huwaweka waumini huru kutoka kwa nguvu ya <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108195\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">dhambi</span>, kifo na uovu.</p><p>Wanaposikiliza na kujifunza, waumini wanapaswa kuweka neno la Mungu katika vitendo. Hii inawaongoza kuepuka kufanya maovu. Pia inawaongoza kuwajali watu wanaohitaji msaada.</p>",
